snippet.title: "I Kicked Him" Amber Heard Admits She Did Not Only Hit Johnny Depp
snippet.description:
"I Kicked Him" Amber Heard Admits She Did Not Only Hit Johnny Depp, but what more did she do?
Amber Heard and Johnny Depp's relationship has seen its ups and downs. The former couple had only been married for two years when they were embroiled in a protracted court battle. The relationship between Amber Heard and Johnny Depp has been nothing short of turbulent. The couple went through it all over their four years together, from the iconic dog smuggling episode to Amber's shocking divorce petition. Of course, there have been claims of abuse, various defamation lawsuits, and numerous court appearances for the two stars since they called their quits.
